hi-bazinga:
I encountered the same problem.
source code : https://github.com/tommy351/hexo/blob/master/lib/plugins/processor/post.js
```
meta.source = data.path;
meta.raw = results.read;
meta.slug = escape(path.match(rBasename)[3]);   //slug:2013-01-01-hello-world
if (meta.date){
  if (!(meta.date instanceof Date)){
    meta.date = moment(meta.date, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss').toDate();
  }
```
if date is defined in YAML, meta.slug will remain  ' 2013-01-01-hello-world ' , the permelink will be  ' 2013/01/01/2013-01-01-hello-world/ '
```
} else {
  var match = getInfoFromFilename(path); // path is splited into: '2013','01','01','hello-world.md'
if (match && match.year && match.month && match.day){
    meta.date = new Date(match.year, match.month - 1, match.day);
    meta.slug = match.title; // match.title : 'hello-world.md'
  } else {
    meta.date = stat.ctime;
  }
}
```
if date is not defined in YAML, meta.slug will be assigned to match.title : ' hello-world.md ', the permelink will be ' 2013/01/01/hello-world.md/ ' 
I tried to change the rBasename and assign the correct post name like 'hello-world' to meta.slug before  if (meta.date),
and delete meta.slug = match.title; in the inner ELSE part, and it works fine now.
.

